  "title": "QAQC Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities :</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and implement Project Quality Plan, Inspection and Testing Plan</li><li>Conduct pre-inspection of work prior to joint inspection with the Client</li><li>Prepare request for inspection for the project</li><li>Compile and submit QAQC documents or records to the client</li><li>Liaise with the client in any issues concerning quality control of the project</li><li>Review and inspect all inspection reports for compliance</li><li>Prepare and monitor the daily activities on site</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements :</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree in Quality Assurance Engineering or other related field</li><li>Minimum 3 years working experience in a QAQC role in a Building Construction industry</li><li>Strong understanding of Quality Management Systems (QMS), testing methodologies and quality standards</li><li>Proficient with QA/QC tools (For example : inspection equipment, defect tracking software and data analysis tools etc)</li></ul><p></p>",
